# ApiService Learning Topics

## High-Level Categories
1. REST API Design
2. Authentication
3. Request/Response Modeling
4. Retrofit Annotations
5. API Security

## Core Concepts Used

### Retrofit Annotations
1. HTTP Methods
  - @GET, @POST, @DELETE
  - Path parameters
  - Headers

2. Data Modeling
  - Request bodies
  - Response handling
  - Suspending functions

### Authentication & Security
1. Token Management
  - JWT handling
  - API key headers
  - User authentication

2. Request Structure
  - User credentials
  - Favorite operations
  - Password reset

### Data Classes
1. Request Models
  - Login/Signup
  - Favorites
  - Password reset

2. Response Models
  - Authentication tokens
  - User data
  - Image data

## Suggested Study Order

1. REST Fundamentals
  - HTTP methods
  - Endpoints
  - Status codes

2. Authentication
  - Token-based auth
  - API keys
  - Security headers

3. Data Transfer
  - Request/Response models
  - Serialization
  - Error handling

4. Advanced Features
  - Coroutines
  - Response mapping
  - Header management

## Key Technologies
- Retrofit
- Kotlin Data Classes
- Coroutines
- HTTP Methods
- JWT

